To finish setting up SUSE OpenStack Cloud 4 you will need to define the network.
To help you with the network configuration refer to the deployment guide and
companion deployment questionnaire.

execute yast2 crowbar

Once your network settings are all defined then continue the crowbar install

execute screen install-suse-cloud

Before you proceed with install-suse-cloud its important that the network
settings are properly defined and that you have everything right otherwise
you will need to start over.
